  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety Study of Eravacycline Compared With Meropenem in Complicated Intra-abdominal Infections</brief_title>
  <acronym>IGNITE4</acronym>
  <official_title>A Phase 3, Randomized, Double-Blind, Double-Dummy, Multicenter, Prospective Study to Assess the Efficacy and Safety of Eravacycline Compared With Meropenem in Complicated Intra-abdominal Infections</official_title>
